        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Negating Emissions to Zero Act of 2021 or the NET Zero Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill extends through 2031 the tax credit for carbon oxide sequestration. It also modifies carbon oxide capture requirements and sets forth a special rule for determining the applicable dollar amount for the deduction of costs relating to direct air capture facilities.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
